<div class="call-to-action">
<h2 id="national-restrictions">National restrictions</h2>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/new-national-restrictions-from-5-november" class="govuk-link">National restrictions</a> apply in England. These have replaced local COVID alert levels (tiers).</p>

<p>You must avoid travelling internationally or within the <abbr title="United Kingdom">UK</abbr> and stay at home, unless you are travelling for work, education or for other <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/new-national-restrictions-from-5-november#travel" class="govuk-link">legally permitted reasons</a>, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>travelling to work where this cannot be done from home</li>
  <li>travelling to education and for caring responsibilities</li>
  <li>hospital, <abbr title="general practitioner">GP</abbr> and other medical appointments or visits where you have had an accident or are concerned about your health</li>
  <li>visiting venues that are open, including essential retail</li>
  <li>exercise, if you need to make a short journey to do so</li>
</ul>
</div>

